            <title>[CAMEL-5137] Timer component does not suspend</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-5137</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A route which begins with a Timer consumer does not suspend the consumer when the route is suspended.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Windows XP and RedHat Linux&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
